item.title: About me
item.author: whuwhm@outlook.com (Felix Wu)
item.description: Hi, I’m Haoming, a web front end developer in Sydney. About me I love learning new skills in web development and other fields as well. I’m always a believer that pushing ourselves out of comfort zone and embrace new technologies is an efficient way to make a better version of ourselves. I’m also a great fun of running. At first, running can be tiring and tedious. But once getting over the hardest part, I can feel the inner peace and the pleasure of runner.
